{"tid":1465212,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[現場］我屌哂班5毛分化撚老母","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T08:32:24.000Z","uid":29302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"053cd0d1399e56be8d3b9bac17780da0c9867a53","tid":1465212,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"成班手足係到努力各有各做，你班冷氣撚做緊乜鳩<br />\n有咩資格批評現場既手足，你有係到面對班旅客咩？<br />\n你有係到捉狗捉公安咩？你有係現場派物資咩？<br />\n乜7都話鬼<br />\n冇大台既活動無論如何都唔可以分化<br />\n唔理做岩定做錯，我地都要去做野，去補救，去幫手<br />\n但唔撚係係屋企涼冷氣分化手足<br />\n5毛我屌你老母為左少少錢出賣人性，睇住收尾果幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d2f4d878b1cf07a1d406a88fb7c1d5a7e513e6","tid":1465212,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"813機場出真槍"},{"pid":"3160cba12dd5342a99f69f6b14fac18c5dc90c77","tid":1465212,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0153e2f54c15ed409255bf6425149d930e435602","tid":1465212,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0381da3142008da2609a2cbd5a405f59d2490505","tid":1465212,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20330b84e388bf26ca4425795bdf153fd52d8878","tid":1465212,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6bbfb04686443a2c50097ea00333e96c522f22","tid":1465212,"uid":29302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"649cf7c6105ea937154d5c